Dialogue: 3,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idioti...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:49.81,0:09:50.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Další.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoi Ayato!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:52.61,0:09:53.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ano!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobře já.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:59.99,0:10:00.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bože.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... Děkujeme za tvoje úsilí!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Yuzuru!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:07.37,0:10:08.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ano!
